20:39.239 --> 20:40.900
- Sangani.
- Sangani.

20:40.990 --> 20:42.776
- Yeah.
- F.B.|. Special Agent Booth.

20:42.867 --> 20:46.109
We’re looking to get some
information on this guy.
Santiago Valmont.

20:46.204 --> 20:47.910
He was spotted here last Tuesday.

20:47.997 --> 20:50.124
Nah, man. I never heard of him.

20:50.208 --> 20:51.698
Really?

20:51.793 --> 20:54.455
We know that you were busted
last year for selling drugs, Poorab.

20:54.546 --> 20:56.252
No, man. No, no, man.
I’m clean, man.

20:56.339 --> 20:58.250
Yo, I’m, like,
“in the program” clean, man.

20:58.341 --> 21:00.332
So, you wouldn’t mind
cooperating with us, right?

21:01.678 --> 21:03.384
Well, yeah, man, yeah.
Damn.

21:03.471 --> 21:06.053
Here you go.
Right there.

21:07.350 --> 21:10.433
This dude’s rockin’
straight-up woman hair.

21:10.520 --> 21:13.353
He’s actually rockin’
no hair at the moment.
He’s dead.

21:14.983 --> 21:17.440
Oh, man, dude. Ugh.

21:17.527 --> 21:20.485
You know what, man?
Yo, my brother, he was workin’
on Tuesday night, right?

21:20.572 --> 21:23.735
He’s in the back makin’ samosas.
I’m-a go get him for you. All right?

21:23.825 --> 21:27.909
Yo, Ronnie!
Hey, man, time to do
some public service, bro.

21:28.037 --> 21:29.902
Agent Booth?
Yeah.

21:29.998 --> 21:31.488
Blue liquid.

21:34.252 --> 21:36.868
The stuff
he was doused in, huh?
Mm-hmm.

21:38.965 --> 21:40.466
Poorab!

21:41.551 --> 21:43.337
[Grunts]

21:43.428 --> 21:44.759
Hey!

21:47.974 --> 21:50.386
[ Grunts ]
All right.

21:50.477 --> 21:52.843
[ Man ] Wow, man.
Did you see
what happened?

21:52.937 --> 21:55.269
Are they cops?
Booth.

21:57.317 --> 21:59.399
Look at that.
That’s a lot of hair.
Yeah.

21:59.486 --> 22:02.398
I don’t think Santiago was
the only one who got scalped.

22:09.537 --> 22:11.949
Okay, great.
Just let me know when
he has his P.D., okay?

22:12.081 --> 22:13.742
Great. Thanks.
Poorab won’t talk?

22:13.833 --> 22:16.825
No, not till he has
his public defender.
This is not what I need.

22:16.920 --> 22:19.457
I got so much
on my plate right now.
I don’t need his grief.

22:19.589 --> 22:21.204
Who? Dr. Brennan?
Huh?

22:21.299 --> 22:22.789
It’s a communication issue,
isn’t it?

22:22.884 --> 22:25.671
You know what, Sweets?
My life is not a game show, all right?

22:25.762 --> 22:28.879
You know, if you don’t deal
with communication issues
right away,

22:28.973 --> 22:32.386
they can fester
and cause serious damage
to a relationship.

22:32.477 --> 22:34.809
It’s not that. ljust—
[ Sighs ]

22:34.896 --> 22:38.559
Look, I think she’s feeling
a little unattractive
since having the baby.

22:38.691 --> 22:40.556
That’s all.
Oh!

22:40.652 --> 22:41.767
“Oh” what?

22:41.861 --> 22:43.897
It’s very common
for a— a new mother...

22:43.988 --> 22:46.400
to experience
a certain degree
of body dysmorphism.

22:46.491 --> 22:47.981
Dysma— What?

22:48.117 --> 22:49.823
Dysmorphism.
Dysmorphism?

22:49.911 --> 22:51.447
Dysmorphism.
What is that?

22:51.538 --> 22:53.620
It’s a condition related
to body image.

22:53.748 --> 22:56.205
Have you told her lately
that she looks—
Of course!

22:56.292 --> 22:58.874
And she does, all right?
All the time I’m telling her
she looks great.

22:58.962 --> 23:02.705
But I just think
that she feels like I’m
shining her on. That’s all.

23:02.799 --> 23:05.040
You need to show her
that she’s wrong.

23:05.134 --> 23:09.969
Buy her something
that, you know, makes her
feel... beautiful.

23:12.684 --> 23:15.050
Cupcakes?
Lingerie.

23:15.144 --> 23:16.850
|— Oh.

23:16.938 --> 23:19.224
It’s a lingerie store.

23:19.357 --> 23:22.190
