Women love lingerie.

23:22.277 --> 23:24.268
| buy it for Daisy
all the time.

23:25.905 --> 23:28.282
You know I’m right.

23:29.158 --> 23:30.864
All right.

23:30.952 --> 23:32.692
There we go.

23:32.829 --> 23:35.821
Sequins, colors.
These are crotchless.

23:35.915 --> 23:39.248
Crotchless. I think
you know a little bit
too much about this.

23:39.335 --> 23:42.372
Daisy’s adventurous.
Huh?

23:42.505 --> 23:44.962
Huh?
You know what? This—
This is a bad idea.

23:45.049 --> 23:46.789
Let’s go.
What?

23:46.884 --> 23:49.296
Perhaps this bralette
is more to your liking.

23:49.387 --> 23:52.595
It comes with these delicious panties.

23:52.682 --> 23:54.388
Ooh.
[Chuckles]

23:54.475 --> 23:56.340
Um, I’m just looking.

23:56.436 --> 23:58.597
If you want something
more intimate—

23:58.730 --> 24:00.686
No!
Yeah, he does.

24:00.773 --> 24:02.764
- What size is she?
- Well, I don’t know.

24:02.859 --> 24:04.440
You see, she just had a baby.

24:04.527 --> 24:07.894
Are we talking apples or melons?

24:07.989 --> 24:09.604
Mangoes.

24:09.741 --> 24:12.448
You lookin’ at her fruit?
I am a doctor.

24:12.535 --> 24:14.196
Just accept the help.

24:14.287 --> 24:17.529
