I don’t need that many.
I’m just looking for one thing.

24:17.624 --> 24:20.661
Actually, one small little thing.
Not too small.

24:20.793 --> 24:22.294
One thing?
Yeah.

24:22.378 --> 24:24.289
For the woman
who just had your baby?

24:24.422 --> 24:26.629
What?
Come on.

24:26.716 --> 24:30.709
If you want
this relationship to last,
you’d better let me help you.

24:30.803 --> 24:33.135
You pulled me away
from examining the bones...

24:33.222 --> 24:35.213
to play with the biggest
hair ball on earth?

24:35.308 --> 24:38.721
It’s one paper, Mr. Vaziri,
not the Nobel Prize.

24:38.811 --> 24:41.268
Did Hodgins tell you?
Angela.

24:41.356 --> 24:43.347
Emilio in the parking garage.

24:43.441 --> 24:45.853
