24:50.156 --> 24:54.445
- [ Device Beeps ]
- Thank you, mid-17th-century
immigrants.

24:54.535 --> 24:56.992
What are those things?
Wool carders.

24:57.080 --> 25:00.447
I got them from
the Colonial New England
diorama.

25:00.541 --> 25:03.328
Now, if these honeys
can separate wool,

25:03.419 --> 25:06.911
then human hair—
human hair should be
a piece of cake.

25:07.006 --> 25:09.622
Beats tweezing.
Carder up, Mr. Vaziri.

25:29.195 --> 25:32.187
Hey, I figure
if we grab a snack now,

25:32.281 --> 25:34.021
we can dish for about
eight minutes,

25:34.117 --> 25:36.199
and then we can pump
later on.

25:36.327 --> 25:39.160
It’s a glamorous life
we lead, isn’t it?
I’m working.

25:39.247 --> 25:41.158
