25:41.249 --> 25:43.285
I got you a grilled-veggie pita,
by the way,

25:43.376 --> 25:45.492
because I know
you’re a wild woman.

25:45.586 --> 25:49.579
I’ve noticed some damage
and scarring that didn’t
show up on the Angelatron.

25:49.674 --> 25:51.210
Oh, really?

25:51.300 --> 25:54.463
Arastoo is gonna be bummed.
He thought he was on a roll.

25:54.554 --> 25:56.715
More importantly,

25:56.806 --> 26:00.845
I got us a reservation
at The Four Winds Spa.

26:00.935 --> 26:03.221
I know. I know.
You’re welcome.

26:03.312 --> 26:06.554
Facials, body scrubs, massages.

26:06.649 --> 26:07.889
Fracturing.

26:07.984 --> 26:10.270
I’m gonna take a pass
on the fracturing.

26:10.361 --> 26:11.862
Are you in?

26:11.946 --> 26:13.937
Itsounds
appealingly indulgent.

26:15.408 --> 26:17.490
There’s an injury
to the victim’s back.

26:17.577 --> 26:20.159
The L4 and L5 show
hairline fracturing.

26:20.246 --> 26:21.952
And there’s no remodeling.

26:22.039 --> 26:24.121
These injuries occurred
at time of death.

26:24.208 --> 26:25.459
Oh.

26:25.543 --> 26:28.706
Dr. Brennan?
I found something
you need to see.

26:30.089 --> 26:32.956
You can see
a dark line of demarcation
near the cut end.

26:33.050 --> 26:34.665
That’s a result
of putrefaction.

26:34.761 --> 26:37.252
Which means the hair
was cut off a corpse.

26:37.346 --> 26:39.758
Is this
Santiago Valmont’s hair?

26:39.849 --> 26:43.433
No. The hair shaft
has a circular cross section
and a thick cuticle.

26:43.519 --> 26:45.100
It didn’t come from a Caucasian.

26:45.188 --> 26:47.019
So, where’s the victim’s hair?

26:47.106 --> 26:48.767
We haven’t found
a match for him yet,

26:48.858 --> 26:51.941
but we have found hair
from 25 different people
in the hair bundle.

26:52.028 --> 26:54.986
- All dead at the time
the hair was removed.
- Twenty-five victims?

26:55.072 --> 26:58.030
Perhaps Dr. Sweets
was right about this being
a ritualistic killing.

26:58.117 --> 27:00.574
Well, if he was hog-tied
in some kind of ceremony,

27:00.661 --> 27:03.869
that would account for
the injuries I found
in the victim’s L4 and L5.

27:03.956 --> 27:05.821
Those didn’t show up
on the Angelatron.

27:05.917 --> 27:07.532
No, they didn’t, Mr. Vaziri.

27:07.627 --> 27:10.619
Sometimes it is best not
to let a machine do your work.

27:10.713 --> 27:14.297
Please reexamine the bones
to see what else you missed
in your quest for notoriety.

27:14.383 --> 27:16.214
Of course.

27:27.438 --> 27:30.020
I’m Tess Levinson.
I’m representing Mr. Sangani.

27:30.107 --> 27:31.813
